commit.message:
Update msvc Makefile
Added note to readme about Python installation. Closes #6

Refactor code (#4)
- Significant cleanup
- Move all python interpreter handling into separate file
- Fix several python thread stability issues
- Fix memory leak in python eval return value handling
- Remove unused tclthread.c
Implement makefile for MSVC compiler. Closes #2

Enable Python2 and Python3 to coexist
Python2 --> tclpython
Python3 --> tclpython3

Remove dependency on symcat.h
Avoid buffer size issue entirely by printing thread ID message in hex.

Initial commit. Jean-Luc Fontaine's tclpython 4.1
